                            <comment id="13858258" author="cheolsoo" created="Sun, 29 Dec 2013 06:22:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lbendig&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lbendig&quot;&gt;lbendig&lt;/a&gt;, thank you for finding this. I see the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have two minor comments on your patch-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Can we generate the input file to local instead of making the test run in mr mode? I prefer local mode to mr mode if possible since the latter is slower.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Can we move FileLocalizer.reset(null) to setup()? That will let not only this test but also every test run w/o a side effect in the future.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I am uploading a patch that addresses my comments and will commit this if you have no objection. Let me know.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13858409" author="rohini" created="Sun, 29 Dec 2013 19:35:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13858465" author="cheolsoo" created="Sun, 29 Dec 2013 22:50:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk. Thank you Lorand and Rohini!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13858467" author="lbendig" created="Sun, 29 Dec 2013 22:58:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, I had no objections. Thank you for the update!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
